OL,3,C'Being alone without support is the
OL,4,Cworst': Life as a homeless teenager
OL,6,FA teenager who was homeless for more
OL,7,Fthan a year says "being alone without
OL,8,Fsupport is the worst".
OL,10,FJordan Brown, 18, lived in temporary
OL,11,Faccommodation in Rhyl after being made
OL,12,Fhomeless in 2023. "I learnt how to
OL,13,Fsurvive on my own", he said.
OL,15,F"When I needed someone, they weren't
OL,16,Fthere, so I just learned to do it on
OL,17,Fmy own."
