OL,3,C'Being alone without support is the
OL,4,Cworst': Life as a homeless teenager
OL,6,FHe added: "It's a pain to see other
OL,7,Fpeople go through that because there's
OL,8,Fnothing I can do to support them, but
OL,9,FI can tell them what it's like and
OL,10,Fthey can avoid it."
OL,12,FJordan has shared his experiences as a
OL,13,F"groundbreaking" bill has been
OL,14,Fpresented to the Senedd on 19 May.
OL,16,FThe draft bill has been in the works
OL,17,Ffor several years and draws on
OL,18,Fexperiences and testimonies from those
OL,19,Fwith lived experience of homelessness,
OL,20,Fas well as charities that provide
OL,21,Fsupport to the homeless.
