OL,3,C'Being alone without support is the
OL,4,Cworst': Life as a homeless teenager
OL,6,FSome of the key points include
OL,7,Fredefining who is considered homeless
OL,8,Fbased on different timeframes, more
OL,9,Ffocus on young people leaving care and
OL,10,Flocal authorities working with people
OL,11,Fearlier.
OL,13,FThe Welsh Government says the Bill is
OL,14,Ffocused on early prevention and
OL,15,Fproviding more tools to support people
OL,16,Finto longer-term homes.
