OL,3,C'Being alone without support is the
OL,4,Cworst': Life as a homeless teenager
OL,6,FAfter being made homeless, Jordan said
OL,7,Fhe spent more than a year living in
OL,8,Ftemporary accommodation in Rhyl. He
OL,9,Fdescribed the conditions at the hostel
OL,10,Fhe lived in.
OL,12,FHe said: "My hostel was full of rats
OL,13,Fand everything. It was just disgusting.
OL,15,F"All I had was a microwave and a
OL,16,Ftoaster. There wasn't a washing
OL,17,Fmachine either."
OL,19,FJordan added that he often saw drug
OL,20,Fdeals taking place.
