OL,3,C'Being alone without support is the
OL,4,Cworst': Life as a homeless teenager
OL,6,F"I saw basically everything you can
OL,7,Fname - XYZ," he explained.
OL,9,F"The fact that I saw all that really
OL,10,Fdid get to my head. At a young age,
OL,11,Fyou shouldn't have to go through that."
OL,13,FThanks to the help of the housing
OL,14,Fassociation Grwp Cynefin's
OL,15,Fhomelessness service, Gorwel, Jordan
OL,16,Fnow has a stable and safe place to
OL,17,Flive. "I wouldn't change it for the
OL,18,Fworld", he said.
OL,20,F"I'm back on my feet now."
