OL,3,C'Being alone without support is the
OL,4,Cworst': Life as a homeless teenager
OL,6,FThe bill has been described by
OL,7,Fcampaigners as "groundbreaking".
OL,9,FThe director of homelessness
OL,10,Forganisation, Cymorth Cymru, Katie
OL,11,FDalton, said: "We engaged with over
OL,12,F300 people with experience of
OL,13,Fhomelessness in the lead-up work to
OL,14,Fthis bill, and it's fantastic to see
OL,15,Fso many of their views and experiences
OL,16,Freflected in the bill.
OL,18,FKatie added: "The bill, as it stands,
OL,19,Fis in really good shape, but the bill
OL,20,Falone will not solve homelessness.
