OL,3,C'Being alone without support is the
OL,4,Cworst': Life as a homeless teenager
OL,6,F"We need to continue building social
OL,7,Fhousing in Wales, so that means that
OL,8,Fthe next government has to have really
OL,9,Fstrong social house building targets.
OL,11,F"There needs to be appropriate funding
OL,12,Fin future Welsh Government budgets for
OL,13,Fboth social housing but also the vital
OL,14,Fsupport services that help people to
OL,15,Faccess and, importantly, maintain that
OL,16,Fhome once they get it."
