OL,3,C'Being alone without support is the
OL,4,Cworst': Life as a homeless teenager
OL,6,F"Every person deserves a safe place to
OL,7,Fcall home, and these reforms bring us
OL,8,Fcloser to making that a reality across
OL,9,FWales," the minister added.
OL,11,F"I'm particularly pleased about what
OL,12,Fthis means for young care leavers. By
OL,13,Fbringing housing and social services
OL,14,Fteams together, we'll ensure these
OL,15,Fyoung people, who are our
OL,16,Fresponsibility, get the support they
OL,17,Fneed.
